   <title title="polyline" />
   The following attributes are supported:
   <ul>
      <li>
         <code>points</code>
      </li>      
      <li>
         <code>stroke</code>
      </li>        
      <li>
         <code>opacity</code>
      </li>     
      <li>
         The attributes for <ref id="Strokes support" />
      </li>                 
   </ul>
   Note that the <code>fill</code> attribute is unsupported. All polylines are not filled.  
   
