   <title title="text" />
   The following attributes are supported:
   <ul>
      <li>
         <code>x</code>
      </li>
      <li>
         <code>y</code>
      </li>        
      <li>
         <code>font-family</code>
      </li>
      <li>
         <code>font-size</code>
      </li>  
      <li>
         <code>font-style</code>
      </li>
      <li>
         <code>text-decoration</code>
      </li>      
      <li>
         <code>text-anchor</code>
      </li>                           
   </ul>   
   
   Note: only the <code>underline</code> and <code>line-through</code> values are supported for the <code>text-decoration</code>
   attribute.
   
   <title level="2" title="tspan" />
   Text can contain <code>tspan</code> elements.
   
   The following attributes are supported:
   <ul>
      <li>
         <code>x</code>
      </li>
      <li>
         <code>y</code>
      </li>        
